query: WITH entities AS (SELECT telegram_id, id FROM customers WHERE (COALESCE((telegram_id, id) > ($3, $2), $2 IS NULL)) ORDER BY telegram_id, id LIMIT $1) SELECT i.id AS "entity_id: CustomerId", e.sequence, e.event, e.recorded_at FROM entities i JOIN customer_events e ON i.id = e.id ORDER BY i.telegram_id, i.id, i.id, e.sequence
